name: Guardian Health & Beauty - Limbang Shopping Centre

reviews.text:
After past experience, pls calculate the total amount when u purchase anything from the outlet.

I paid without calculate the total price  and shocked when I scan the reciept. I questioned the staff and she said I saw the wrong label. The label was stated clearly assorted shampoo buy 1 get 1 free.  Another shampoo that I regular buy, the label said 18 dollars yet she charged me over  22 dollars... said no discount in blur look. Then I show her the display..she quickly removed the sale label. She told me my refund only can receive 1 week later when the reciept stated for cheque then required 1 week and bb net refund will directly credited back to the account.
open timing so slow supposed to be opened at 9 but i waited more than 10 min still haven't open.
It states OPEN in google but when u go down there it is close! No notice no nothing.
